  "description": {
    "en": "Create and update a counter that counts the number of left turns against the number of right turns. Whenever you can turn left and right, choose the direction that (according to the counter) has been chosen less often. Otherwise, go straight or turn in the only free direction. If there is a tie, go right first. (The map for this task does not contain any dead ends).",
